			<h2 class="section-title" style="text-align:left; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">How a 34-Agent Brokerage Could Cut Transaction Coordination Time by 71%</h2>
			<p style="opacity:0.6; font-size:0.85rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Multi-location brokerage &nbsp;·&nbsp; Deployed in 5 weeks &nbsp;·&nbsp; Tools: Make, OpenAI, Google Workspace, Slack, DocuSign</p>

			<div style="background: rgba(74,222,128,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.25); border-radius: 6px; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem; font-size:0.85rem; line-height:1.5; opacity:0.85;">
			<strong>Hypothetical engagement.</strong> This scenario is based on the types of problems we solve and the workflows we deploy. It reflects real processes, real tools, and realistic outcomes — not a specific client engagement.
